name: Star Guardian Neeko
description:
Star Guardian Neeko

Model Variants

You can download the variants in the download section. These are trained for front-posing.

  • WDv1.3

  • PVC

    • This turns Neeko into a figurine!

  • AnythingV3

I also have an underfit/general version that will merge with most models (e.g. NSFW) in the download section.

Creating your own variant

Grab a model from anywhere & go to "Checkpoint Merger" in web-ui. Set A to the downloaded model (if it's front posing, use the main download, otherwise use the underfit model). Set C to WDv1.3. Set B to the model you want to add it to. Set a custom name, multiplier to 1, select "add difference". Save as fp16 to save space.

Tags that help

star guardian neeko, ((orange hair)), green hair, multicolored hair, pink hair, pink tail, green hands, green feet, symbol-shaped pupils

How to create a character model like this!

https://www.reddit.com/r/StableDiffusion/comments/107dw0a/creating_a_specific_character_via_dreambooth/
